moduleMetadataJson.name: Windows Escalate Get System via Administrator
moduleMetadataJson.description:
This module uses the builtin 'getsystem' command to escalate
        the current session to the SYSTEM account from an administrator
        user account.
author: hdm <x@hdm.io>
